E COMBINING LORA WITH PREFIX TUNING
LoRA can be naturally combined with existing preÔ¨Åx-based approaches. In this section, we evaluate two combinations of LoRA and variants of preÔ¨Åx-tuning on WikiSQL and MNLI.
LoRA+PreÔ¨ÅxEmbed (LoRA+PE) combines LoRA with preÔ¨Åx-embedding tuning, where we insert lp + li special tokens whose embeddings are treated as trainable parameters. For more on preÔ¨Åxembedding tuning, see Section 5.1.
LoRA+PreÔ¨ÅxLayer (LoRA+PL) combines LoRA with preÔ¨Åx-layer tuning. We also insert lp + li special tokens; however, instead of letting the hidden representations of these tokens evolve natu-
